      <title>澳大利亚主权财富基金因风险资产上涨而增长；对降息持谨慎态度</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/australias-sovereign-wealth-fund-grows-risk-asset-rally-cautious-about-rate-cuts-2024-01-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二公布的业绩显示，受全球股市上涨的提振，澳大利亚主权财富基金的业绩在 2023 年最后一个季度出现反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/australias-sovereign-wealth-fund-grows-risk-asset-rally-cautious-about-rate-cuts-2024-01-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 23:02:46 GMT</pubDate>
