      <title>美英空袭也门胡塞武装地下储存库</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-britain-strike-underground-houthi-storage-site-yemen-2024-01-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[五角大楼表示，美国和英国周一针对也门胡塞武装针对红海航运进行了新一轮打击，目标是地下储存地点、导弹和胡塞武装的其他军事能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-britain-strike-underground-houthi-storage-site-yemen-2024-01-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 22:45:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
